    "Likewise, it will be noteworthy to delve deeper into how ChatGPT could impact teaching and learning in disciplines such as Mathematics and Science.",
    "In addition, a contrastive text analysis of AI-produced texts and humanproduced texts can prove beneficial to better the performance of ADWTs or to better distinguish the features of AI-generated text vis-a-vis human-generated text.",
    "Additionally, a more in-depth study on the various strategies educators and students employ to mitigate threats of using ADWTs in various specific disciplines and tasks may be conducted to document the nuances and intricacies in these unique contexts as these tools are constantly being improved.",
